&lt;li&gt;Own organic and paid acquisition strategy across all channels, including direct oversight of our paid acquisition agency — setting strategy, budget allocation, and performance expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive developer community acquisition accross Reddit, Hacker News, dev-focused communities, technical content, GitHub presence, and DevRel-adjacent programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product-Led Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
