&lt;li&gt;Work directly with Product and Engineering to prioritize self-serve improvements and advocate for PLG in planning cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI/ML Segment Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
