&lt;li&gt;Own the corporate narrative and translate it into channel strategy, content, and partnerships targeting our strategic markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and develop go-to-market programs for the key strategic ICPs: developer tools integrations, community presence, co-marketing, and technical content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
