&lt;p data-start=&quot;1260&quot; data-end=&quot;1524&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Product Manager to lead strategy, execution, and growth for Backblaze’s Computer Backup product across consumer and business offerings. This role will own the roadmap for our desktop backup clients, web experiences, and associated admin tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1526&quot; data-end=&quot;1939&quot;&gt;This is a highly hands-on role on a small, focused team. You will need to make thoughtful decisions about where to invest resources, align stakeholders around clear priorities, and drive progress through influence, collaboration, and conviction. Success in this role requires strong product instincts, data-informed decision making, and the ability to bring cross-functional teams together around a shared vision.&lt;/p&gt;
