&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;h3na80&quot; data-start=&quot;1812&quot; data-end=&quot;1913&quot;&gt;Align and normalize data across systems, including Salesforce, product systems, and support tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;xbqtr4&quot; data-start=&quot;1914&quot; data-end=&quot;1969&quot;&gt;Build clean, reusable datasets for analytics and BI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;c1tacl&quot; data-start=&quot;1970&quot; data-end=&quot;2159&quot;&gt;Define and standardize core SaaS metrics, including Net Revenue Retention (NRR), Gross Revenue Retention (GRR), expansion, contraction, churn, renewal forecasting, and pipeline coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1nltk0e&quot; data-start=&quot;2160&quot; data-end=&quot;2265&quot;&gt;Partner with Customer Success, Revenue Operations, Sales, and Finance teams to drive revenue insights&lt;/li&gt;
